<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-60-0896 </DOCNO><TEXT>It is argued that renewable energy should be developed rapidly for islands.Renewable energy sources match the ecology of islands, the economicsof the capital intensive equipment is improved by low operational costs,cash flow and employment on the islands is increased. Examples are givenof wind turbine generators, photovoltaic power modules, biofuel, wavepower devices and energy planning in an island context which have contributedto innovative techniques which may be developed in products for the worldmarket. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>